{"tid":2338790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警針對Shady Acres 每日查牌一小時","createTime":"2020-12-24T08:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T16:25:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":70,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"23b71003f9930134bd3fff4b1e16514e34074409","tid":2338790,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/DD3VQ4ETGVBDZKIAMGZF5SCZMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FDD3VQ4ETGVBDZKIAMGZF5SCZMY%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=1f1591be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FDD3VQ4ETGVBDZKIAMGZF5SCZMY%2F&h=7804609a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/DD3VQ4ETGVBDZKIAMGZF5SCZMY/</a><br />\n<br />\n警針對Shady Acres 每日查牌一小時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YzCUhAcMOup7I6oXQFg1IWzNTUc=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SCYRUNT6PZDVNPLXZZQSHI63BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYzCUhAcMOup7I6oXQFg1IWzNTUc%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSCYRUNT6PZDVNPLXZZQSHI63BE.jpg&h=1cb3eac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自特首林鄭月娥。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YzCUhAcMOup7I6oXQFg1IWzNTUc=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SCYRUNT6PZDVNPLXZZQSHI63BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYzCUhAcMOup7I6oXQFg1IWzNTUc%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSCYRUNT6PZDVNPLXZZQSHI63BE.jpg&h=1cb3eac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■卑利街西式餐廳Shady Acres每日都被警方針對式查牌。<br />\n<br />\n下午6時後禁堂食法令橫跨。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n巡警一直殺上蘇豪區，在傍晚6。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ot0_3uSS5XyEut9GlNXdassSXcI=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTTQER453ZAAZN6ZPFGMEMGRQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOt0_3uSS5XyEut9GlNXdassSXcI%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTTQER453ZAAZN6ZPFGMEMGRQA.jpg&h=b7170ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有卑利街餐廳負責人認為警方巡查只為展示威權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30人掃場呼喝食客<br />\n<br />\n開業僅年半的Shady Acres一名負責人表示，警方針對式巡查自9月起日日發生，有時更一日數次，每次查半小時至近句鐘。Shady Acres每日供應堂食僅六小時，但當中至少一個鐘已無法做生意。警方每次到場都十分高姿態，一時將警車泊正店門外，一時在店外拉起封鎖線，逾半時間更有30警員齊走進店內，數目多於限聚令下的五成入座率要求。<br />\n<br />\n警員曾經無故指令全場食客戴上口罩肅靜，及出示身份證供登記，態度欠佳，又無理禁止店員致電律師，更在未到禁堂食時間就呼喝道「叫你閂門啊！」<br />\n<br />\n負責人稱，店舖從未就社會議題表態，「又無針對警察」，大嘆不明所以。餐廳生意已大跌八成，他諮詢過律師但無可跟進行動，若聖誕新年情況持續，勢必倒閉。<br />\n<br />\n警方的回覆並無正面回應為何針對該店所處的史丹頓街與荷李活道之間一段卑利街，僅稱中區警區在過去數月加強巡查。<br />\n<br />\n香港中小企食店聯盟召集人林瑞華說，所有食肆一持酒牌，警方就有權隨時進入查牌，店東只能被動地配合，「佢原意就係想你做唔落去」。<br />\n<br />\n中西區區議員伍凱欣認為，如警方未曾發現店家違規，就有責任主動交代該店是否常收投訴，「係咪好多人喺McDonald&rsquo;s外食包，McDonald&rsquo;s員工又要出去趕先？」否則警方行動難以服眾。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄧溢禧"},{"pid":"25de100093d864ebf4de42e56900a1e6da31fad9","tid":2338790,"uid":70786,"like":123,"dislike":1,"score":122,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"附近係咪有死黑警開嘅酒吧<br />\n想用公權力搞死競爭對手呀？"},{"pid":"f69326b043691dd4ca980c2a8f5208268037e2c1","tid":2338790,"uid":8921,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:01:19.000Z","msg":"中環多家食肆反映，近期每逢周末都有<span class=\"red\"><strong>警犬</strong></span>滋擾，由蘭桂坊一直殺上蘇豪區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hk